reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Awesome for this price!
reviews.reviewText: I sheet mask daily, sometimes more, so this was a good set to have handy. While you can't really tell a difference from mask to mask once opened, it's still fun to have the variety to choose from and have a ton of sheet masks handy. I like that the masks come adhered to a plastic sheet you peel the mask off of, feels more expensive idk why. You get tons of extra essense in each pouch that I use to get another round out of the mask or for my neck, arms etc. Overall I would definitely buy again, worth every penny and more

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The most moisture in a mask.
reviews.reviewText: I am a sheet mask fanatic. These by far are the best ones I have found. The sheet mask itself is not thick, it’s almost like tissue thin mask. The amount of essence and product that is packed into the little packages is amazing. Highly highly recommend these. Five stars for sure.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: So many different scents to choose from, and each is clearly marked with what they are specifically geared for.Having such a wide variety is great for when you have a girls night or a spa party and everyone can choose their own favorites or what their particular skin needs are. Obviously these are not going to be as high-end as some other brands, but they do a good job for basic moisturizing and you definitely can't beat the bargain price for so many masks.
